_sText:
A completely rebuilt version of ctf_2fort (Team-Fortress 2) for Counter-Strike Source with more details, color correction, env sounds and good frames. The Map was originally made for a small funmap contest from thewall.de .

Terror starts with a AK46, CTs with a M4 (and of course a knive and pistol) 

Custom Ground Textures, custom Sun and every other custom texture (like the tweaked models) are made by me.



Made by Michael 'Term!nator525' Z.
www.michael-z.info
